TITLE: Executing Tinybird Migration Steps
DESCRIPTION: Commands for pushing new datasource schema, running backfill operations, and managing migration pipes. This sequence ensures data consistency during schema updates.
SOURCE: https://github.com/openstatusHQ/openstatus/blob/main/packages/tinybird/README.md#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
