LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const limit = 40;
const offset = limit * cursor;

const data = await sql`
  SELECT * FROM table 
  ORDER BY timestamp DESC 
  LIMIT ${limit} 
  OFFSET ${offset}
`;
```

