TITLE: Configuring Litestream for Database Replication
DESCRIPTION: A YAML configuration for Litestream that sets up database replication to an S3-compatible storage bucket. The configuration specifies the path to the SQLite database and provides connection details for the Cloudflare R2 storage service.
SOURCE: https://github.com/openstatusHQ/openstatus/blob/main/apps/web/src/content/posts/introducing-goatstack.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
dbs:
  - path: /data/db
    replicas:
      - type: s3
        endpoint: https://${CLOUDFLARE_R2_ACCOUNT_ID}.r2.cloudflarestorage.com/
        bucket: goat-stack
        access-key-id: ${CLOUDFLARE_R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID}
        secret-access-key: ${CLOUDFLARE_R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY}
```

