TITLE: Monitor Cost Calculation
DESCRIPTION: Mathematical calculation showing the monthly execution units and cost for running monitors on Vercel's Edge Functions across multiple regions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/openstatusHQ/openstatus/blob/main/apps/web/src/content/posts/migration-backend-from-vercel-to-fly.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
6 (10 min monitors) * 24 * 30 * 3 (average execution unit per monitor) * 6 (number of regions) = 77,760 executions units per month

77,600 * (2/1,000,000) = 0.15c per monitor monthly
```

